lead_paragraph: Defending champion Jelena Jankovic moved into the semifinals of Guangzhou Open after defeating Sabine Lisicki 7-6 (4), 6-4 in the quarterfinals on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Jankovic Marches Into Guangzhou Open Semifinals
